<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.6">
<l>mattak kaḷiṟṟu vacutēvar tammuṭai</l>
<l>cittam piriyaita tēvaki taṉvayiṟṟi</l>
<l>lattattiṉ pattānāḷ tōṉṟiya vaccutaṉ</l>
<l>mutta miruntavā kāṇīrē mukiḻnakai yīrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You smiling [ladies], see the way the penis of Acyuta is,</l>
<l>who appeared on the 10th day of Hastam from the womb of Devakī,</l>
<l>who was not separate from the mind of Vasudeva with frenzied elephants.</l>
<l>Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
